利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 去世：呼吁制定法律“保护业内艺术家心理健康”的请愿书已获得近 40,000 个签名https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-death-petition-safeguarding-mental-health-artists-3805132?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=liam-paynes-death-petition-safeguarding-mental-健康艺术家Liberty DunworthTue, 22 Oct 2024 12:32:41 +0000 Music NewsNews..Let’s Talk – mental healthPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3805132 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="利亚姆·佩恩在舞台上表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>莎朗·奥斯本、布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀等人强调了年轻艺术家面临的压力</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-death-petition-safeguarding-mental-health-artists-3805132">利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 去世后：呼吁制定法律“保护业内艺术家心理健康”的请愿书已获得近 40,000 个签名，</a>最先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="利亚姆·佩恩在舞台上表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一项新的请愿书已经发起，呼吁制定新的法律来保障音乐行业艺术家的心理健康。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：单向明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>请愿书是在<a href="https://www.change.org/p/enact-legislation-to-safeguard-artists-mental-health-in-the-entertainment-industry" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Change.Org 网站</a>上发起的，其背景是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne</a> ) 于上周三（10 月 16 日）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯一家酒店的三楼阳台坠落</a>身亡。</p><p>目前签名数量已超过4万，呼吁加大力度“保护艺人”，为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/lets-talk">娱乐</a>圈的艺人提供更多支持。</p><p> “最近利亚姆·佩恩和其他许多人一样悲惨死亡的消息传出，娱乐业需要承担责任，并对他们的艺术家的福利负责，”请愿书的创建者 Day Kv 写道（ <a href="https://www.change.org/p/enact-legislation-to-safeguard-artists-mental-health-in-the-entertainment-industry" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处签名</a>）。</p><p> “我们寻求立法者制定立法，保护业内艺术家的心理健康，并定期进行心理健康检查、充足的休息时间以及心理健康专业人员在场，包括在创作期间提供持续的支持。他们的职业生涯”。</p><p>佩恩在两年前 14 岁时首次试镜后，在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-x-factor">The X Factor</a></em>的 2010 年系列节目中作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>的一员而声名鹊起。 </p><figure id="attachment_3804331" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804331" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804331" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3804331" class="wp-caption-text"> 2022 年的利亚姆·佩恩。（摄影：JC Olivera/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>他还公开了过去与毒瘾和心理健康的斗争。早在 2021 年，这位独唱家和前 One Direction 成员在史蒂文·巴特利特 (Steven Bartlett) 的<em>《首席执行官日记</em>》播客上发表了讲话，并回忆了他在 One Direction 期间“不太喜欢自己”的经历。</p><p>他接着谈到了“一些我绝对从未公开谈论过的事情”（根据<a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/liam-payne-petition-law-change-entertainment-industry-singer-one-direction-death-b1189057.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《标准》</em></a> ），以及他在公众视野中感受到的挣扎。</p><p>该活动发起之际，引发了一场关于年轻艺术家面临的压力的广泛讨论，以及多位名人呼吁采取行动。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guy-chambers-calls-on-the-music-industry-to-stop-putting-teenagers-in-pop-groups-following-liam-paynes-death-3804414">例如，词曲作家盖伊·钱伯斯 (Guy Chambers) 最近呼吁音乐界停止让未成年人加入男孩乐队</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-on-the-struggles-of-liam-payne-his-trials-and-tribulations-were-very-similar-to-mine-3804014">罗比·威廉姆斯 (Robbie Williams)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-on-the-struggles-of-liam-payne-his-trials-and-tribulations-were-very-similar-to-mine-3804014">则表示，佩恩的“考验和磨难与我的非常相似”</a> ——提到了他作为一名青少年时 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-opens-up-about-past-self-harming-3528952">的自残和抑郁史。</a>前男子组合成员。</p><p>同样， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-accuses-music-industry-of-letting-down-liam-payne-3803983">莎朗·奥斯本指责音乐产业“让佩恩失望”</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-says-music-industry-puts-enormous-pressures-on-young-people-following-liam-paynes-death-3804313">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀则补充说音乐产业“给年轻人带来了巨大的压力”</a> 。</p><p>与 One Direction 一起参加选秀节目的前<em>X Factor</em>选手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Katie-Waissel">凯蒂·维塞尔 (Katie Waissel</a> ) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katie-waissel-calls-for-more-care-and-support-for-young-artists-after-death-of-liam-payne-the-focus-remained-on-profits-rather-than-the-people-3803888">呼吁更多“对年轻艺术家的关心和支持</a>”，同季获得第二名的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rebecca-ferguson">丽贝卡·弗格森 (Rebecca Ferguson</a> ) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rebecca-ferguson-speaks-out-on-exploitation-and-profiteering-of-young-stars-in-liam-payne-tribute-3803708">在发言的同时也向佩恩表示敬意反对“对年轻明星的剥削和牟取暴利”。</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3804476" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804476" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804476" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_liampayne_hydepark_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩守夜海德公园" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_liampayne_hydepark_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_liampayne_hydepark_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_liampayne_hydepark_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_liampayne_hydepark_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_liampayne_hydepark_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_liampayne_hydepark_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3804476" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年 10 月 20 日，伦敦海德公园的彼得潘雕像旁展示着前 One Direction 歌手利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 的照片和笔记（图片来源：JUSTIN TALLIS / AFP via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>大约在同一时间，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Victoria-Canal">维多利亚·卡纳尔(Victoria Canal)</a>回忆起她曾经<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victoria-canal-on-the-lethality-of-the-internet-and-liam-payne-just-days-before-his-death-liam-was-relentlessly-torn-apart-online-for-dancing-at-niall-horans-show-3804204">“绝望”地想要获得佩恩曾经拥有的成功，现在感觉自己被“这个行业‘成功’的承诺所欺骗”。</a></p><p>自从佩恩去世的消息传出后，One Direction 的幸存成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zayn-malik">扎恩·马利克 (Zayn Malik)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/niall-horan">尼尔·霍兰 (Niall Horan)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/louis-tomlinson">路易斯·汤姆林森 (Louis Tomlinson)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯 (Harry Styles)</a>发表了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-speak-out-on-the-death-of-liam-payne-were-completely-devastated-3803904">一份联合声明，请求时间“哀悼并处理失去我们深爱的兄弟”。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-fans-hold-vigils-for-liam-payne-in-liverpool-3804346">世界各地也出现了球迷为佩恩守夜的活动，包括在佩恩去世的利物浦</a>和阿根廷，佩恩的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-father-reads-fan-tributes-outside-argentinian-hotel-where-he-died-3804283">父亲杰夫加入了卡萨苏尔酒店外的人群</a>，感谢聚集在一起纪念他儿子的球迷。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">在整个音乐界，其他人都向佩恩表示了敬意</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shawn-mendes-dedicates-heart-of-gold-to-liam-payne-3804271">肖恩·门德斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-maggie-rogers-pay-tribute-to-liam-payne-with-tender-cover-of-one-directions-night-changes-3804224">玛吉·罗杰斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rita-ora-performs-tearful-liam-payne-duet-hours-after-his-death-3803926">丽塔·奥拉</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-comments-on-liam-paynes-death-life-is-precious-3803700">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>。上周，佩恩的前伴侣、佩恩七岁儿子贝尔的母亲<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cheryl-cole">谢丽尔</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cheryl-indescribably-painful-death-liam-payne-please-give-liam-little-dignity-he-has-left-3804228">谈到了这一“难以形容的痛苦”损失</a>，并敦促人们“给予利亚姆仅存的一点尊严”。</p><p>这并不是音乐行业中心理健康问题第一次成为人们关注的焦点。去年 12 月，音乐家慈善机构 Help Musicians 警告称，过去两年参与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/lets-talk">心理健康</a>服务的人数<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mental-health-charity-help-musicians-sees-200-per-cent-increase-in-service-engagement-3557069">增加了 200%，</a>引发了讨论。</p><p>就在两个月前，音乐界人士<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pressure-cooker-impact-of-touring-on-mental-health-needs-addressing-but-help-is-at-hand-3512555">向<em>《NME》</em>谈到巡演可能对音乐家产生的“危险”和“高压锅”影响</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3803524" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803524" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803524" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803524" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩.图片来源：Karwai Tang/WireImage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>此前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lewis-capaldi-mental-health-break-following-glastonbury-set-3460913">刘易斯·卡帕尔迪 (Lewis Capaldi)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-cancels-upcoming-us-tour-dates-to-look-after-my-own-mental-health-3308481">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shawn-mendes-cancels-remainder-of-his-world-tour-due-to-mental-health-struggles-3278234">肖恩·门德斯</a>(Shawn Mendes) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wet-leg-explain-missed-us-shows-due-to-mental-and-physical-health-issues-3309552">Wet Leg</a>等大牌艺术家都以心理健康问题为由取消了演出。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/editors">编辑</a>吉他手 Justin Lockey 也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/editors-justin-lockey-to-sit-out-of-bands-summer-tour-due-to-struggles-with-anxiety-3232592">因“与焦虑作斗争”而缺席了乐队 2022 年夏季的约会</a>，他告诉<em>NME</em> ：“这可能是一种非常孤立、孤独和奇怪的存在。你与地球上大多数其他人的生活方式不同。”</p><p>去年二月，由已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-specials">Specials</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/terry-hall">Terry Hall</a>倡导的心理健康慈善机构 Tonic <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tonic-mental-health-charity-interview-terry-hall-babyshambles-adam-ficek-3395449">向<em>《NME》</em>讲述了他们为音乐行业从业者提供的重要服务</a>，以及他们如何“帮助我们社区中许多孤立和弱势的人”。</p><p> Hall <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-specials-terry-hall-dies-aged-63-cause-tributes-3369212">于 2022 年 12 月去世</a>，Tonic 首席执行官 Steph Langan 在接受<em>NME</em>采访时解释了“从一开始”就有 Hall 冠军意味着什么，特别是作为一名<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-sharing-this-clip-terry-hall-discussing-mental-health-3371091">经常谈论自己挣扎的</a>艺术家。</p><p>最近，独奏艺术家、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/babyshambles">Babyshambles</a>鼓手和心理治疗师 Adam Ficek 分享了一份关于音乐和心理健康的报告。当时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babyshambles-dr-adam-ficek-shares-report-on-music-and-mental-health-its-business-but-the-product-is-a-human-being-3757294">他告诉<em>《NME》</em> ，“音乐家们总是陷入正式结构化支持系统的缝隙中”</a> 。</p><p> “这项研究是我自己在音乐行业以及在临床实践中与我合作的音乐家的经验的直接结果，”他说。 “我想为其他音乐家提供一个平台，让他们讲述自己关于心理健康的故事，以及他们的各种音乐行业经验如何帮助或阻碍心理健康。”</p><h2><strong>如需心理健康方面的进一步帮助和建议：</strong></h2><ul><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/am-i-depressed-how-to-tell-2067753" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“我有抑郁症吗？” – 有关心理健康以及下一步该做什么的帮助和建议</a></li><li><a href="https://musicindustrytherapists.com/">MITC – 音乐家行业治疗师的集体</a></li><li><a href="https://www.tonicmusic.co.uk/tonic-rider" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TONIC Rider – 为音乐行业专业人士提供定制培训和支持</a></li><li><a href="https://www.helpmusicians.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Help Musicians UK – 为音乐家提供全天候心理健康支持和建议</a></li><li><a href="https://www.musicsupport.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">音乐支持组织 – 为与酗酒、成瘾或心理健康问题作斗争的音乐家提供帮助和支持</a></li><li><a href="https://www.youngminds.org.uk/?gclid=CIuC-9ye69ICFQYo0wodX48KPA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YOUNG MINDS – 年轻人健康和福祉的代言人</a></li><li><a href="https://www.thecalmzone.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CALM——反对悲惨生活的运动</a></li><li><a href="https://www.samaritans.org/how-we-can-help/contact-samaritan/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">撒玛利亚人 – 每天 24 小时提供保密支持</a></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-death-petition-safeguarding-mental-health-artists-3805132">利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 去世后：呼吁制定法律“保护业内艺术家心理健康”的请愿书已获得近 40,000 个签名，</a>最先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
