s="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3772795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Bloc-Party@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Bloc Party的Kele Okereke在2024年演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Bloc-Party@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Bloc-Party@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Bloc-Party@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Bloc-Party@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Bloc-Party@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Bloc-Party@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3772795" class="wp-caption-text"> Bloc Party 的 Kele Okereke 将于 2024 年表演。图片来源：Kieran Frost/Redferns/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> 《Silent Alarm》并不是明年夏天唯一一张在坦普尔纽萨姆公园完整播出的专辑。就在 Bloc Party 作为全天活动的一部分登上舞台几天后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaiser-chiefs-announce-homecoming-employment-20th-anniversary-show-with-razorlight-the-cribs-and-more-3799217">Kaiser Chiefs 将前往利兹举办一场大型返校演出</a>，庆祝“就业”20 周年。</p><p>这将是他们在家乡迄今为止最盛大的演出，并得到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/razorlight">Razorlight</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cribs">The Cribs</a>等乐队的支持。</p><p>在其他 Bloc Party 新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bloc-partys-kele-okereke-shares-new-single-and-announces-album-the-singing-winds-pt-3-and-2025-uk-tour-3797690">Okereke 最近宣布了一张新的个人专辑《The Singing Winds Pt.》。 3”</a>并分享了新单曲“It Wasn&#39;t Meant To Be”。</p><p>这张唱片定于一月发行，将是名为“The Elements”的系列中的第三张，该系列是 Bloc 党主唱在封锁期间创作的一系列个人专辑。在宣布之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bloc-partys-kele-pays-homage-to-london-with-new-solo-single-hometown-edge-3781991">他分享了《Hometown Edge》作为主打单曲</a>。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bloc-party-to-play-silent-alarm-in-full-at-live-at-leeds-2025-3805050">Bloc Party 将在 2025 年利兹现场演出中完整演奏《Silent Alarm》，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
